WEBVTT

00:04:29.822 --> 00:04:30.677
weight loss,

00:04:30.677 --> 00:04:31.737
sleeplessness,

00:04:31.737 --> 00:04:33.515
and irritability.

00:04:33.515 --> 00:04:34.793
But most of the time,

00:04:34.793 --> 00:04:38.603
the endocrine system manages to keep 
our bodies in a state of balance.

00:04:38.603 --> 00:04:40.867
And through its constant regulation,

00:04:40.867 --> 00:04:45.189
it drives the changes that ultimately
help us become who we are.